     H            Y.
     F** JYURR9 **********************************
     F*    REORGANIZE JYUPPML                    *
     F*    T.SAKAKI                 2015.08.04   *
     F********************************** JYURR9 **
     FJYUPPML UF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  INITIALIZE
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@RUNS  1
     C                     MOVEL*OFF      P@RUNS
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     K@YMD
     C           K#AGDP    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@YY
     C                     KFLD           K@MM
     C                     KFLD           K@DD
     C           K#AGDP    CHAINAGDPL12              98
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C           F8YOBI    IFEQ 7
     C                     MOVEL*ON       P@RUNS
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     SUB  1         K@MM
     C           K@MM      IFLE *ZERO
     C                     ADD  12        K@MM
     C                     SUB  1         K@YY
     C                     ENDIF
      * ONE YEAR BEFORE
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     W@YMD
     C                     SUB  1         W@YY
      * 6 MONTHS BEFORE
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     @@YMD
     C                     SUB  6         @@MM
     C           @@MM      IFLE *ZERO
     C                     ADD  12        @@MM
     C                     SUB  1         @@YY
     C                     ENDIF
      * 3 MONTHS BEFORE
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     ZZYMD
     C                     SUB  3         ZZMM
     C           ZZMM      IFLE *ZERO
     C                     ADD  12        ZZMM
     C                     SUB  1         ZZYY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZZYY      ZMYY
     C                     Z-ADDZZMM      ZMMM
     C                     Z-ADDZZDD      ZMDD
     C                     Z-ADD1         ZMID
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *HD
     I                                        1   1 IHKBN
     I                                       46  50 IHREC
      *DT
     I                                        1   1 IDKBN
      *TO
     I                                        1   1 ITKBN
     I                                        2   6 ITREC
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   20TKOTI
     I                                        3   40TKOMI
     I                                        5   60TKOSE
     I                                        7  100TKOYY
     I                                       11  120TKOMM
     I                                       13  140TKODD
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PREC   100
     C                     PARM           PERR    1
     C                     PARM           PCNT    5
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WNO     50
      *----------*
      * CHECK HD *
      *----------*
     C           IHKBN     IFEQ 'H'
     C                     MOVE IHREC     WHREC   50
     C           PREC      IFNE WHREC
     C                     MOVEL'E'       PERR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------*
      * CHECK DT
      *----------*
     C           IDKBN     IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ADD  1         WCNT    50
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------*
      * CHECK TO
      *----------*
     C           ITKBN     IFEQ 'T'
     C                     MOVE ITREC     WTREC   50
     C           WNO       IFNE WTREC
     C                     MOVEL'E'       PERR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WCNT      PCNT
